RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
URL: https://github.com/flh3/CR2
BugReports: https://github.com/flh3/CR2/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports: 
    stats,
    lme4,
    nlme,
    Matrix
